name: SCIPUrologicalPerinealProceduresWithPotentialNeedOfIndwellingCatheters
title: SCIP Urological/Perineal procedures with potential need of indwelling catheters
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This set of values contains  urological and perineal procedures.),(Data Element Scope: The intent of this data element is to identify patients who have had a urological and perineal procedure.  Using the Quality Data Model, this particular element will map to the Procedure category.),(Inclusion Criteria: Include codes that identify patients with urological and perineal procedures. This is a grouping of ICD 10 PCS, ICD 9 CM and SNOMED CT codes.),(Exclusion Criteria: None.)
